::Ramulus::

Ramulus opens his eyes. He had closed and shut the tightly during the 
landing. He forces his fists opens, the knuckles white from clutching the 
seat so tightly. His face was almost completely white, and he was taking 
shallow breaths.

"Huh? What?" he asks Brix in a shaken voice, the spinning room slowing down 
slightly, "Well, I think computer boards might be best to get right away, 
they are the most needed."
